</reading-questions>

<exercises>
<exercise>
  <statement>
    <p>
      In each of the following, suppose the augmented matrix for a linear system has been reduced to the following RREF. Write down the solution(s) to the system (if they exist).
      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            <m>
              \left[\begin{array}{@{}ccc|c@{}} 
              1 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp -4 \\
              0 \amp 1 \amp 0 \amp 5 \\
              0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp 0  
              \end{array}\right]
            </m>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <m>
              \left[\begin{array}{@{}ccc|c@{}} 
              1 \amp -2 \amp 0 \amp 2 \\
              0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp -3 \\
              0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 0
               \end{array}\right]
            </m>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <m>
              \left[\begin{array}{@{}ccc|c@{}} 
              1 \amp 0 \amp -3 \amp 0 \\
              0 \amp 1 \amp 5 \amp 0 \\
              0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 1
               \end{array}\right]
            </m>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <m>
              \left[\begin{array}{@{}ccccc|c@{}} 
              1 \amp 0 \amp 2 \amp -4 \amp 0 \amp 7 \\
              0 \amp 1 \amp 9 \amp -1 \amp 0 \amp -4 \\
              0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp 4
               \end{array}\right]
            </m>
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            The only solution is <m>(-4,5,0)</m>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            The solutions can be written parametrically as
            <me>
              \begin{cases} x_1 = 2x_2 + 2 \\ x_2 \text{ is free} \\ x_3 = -3. \end{cases}
            </me>            
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            There are no solutions.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            The solutions can be written parametrically as 
            <me>
              \begin{cases} 
              x_1 = -2x_3 + 4x_4 + 7 \\ 
              x_2 = -9x_3 + x_4 - 4 \\ 
              x_3 \text{ is free} \\ 
              x_4 \text{ is free} \\
              x_5 = 4.
              \end{cases}
            </me>            
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </p>
  </answer>
</exercise>
